CustomField.description: Used during interpretation processing to exclude an entry from Minimum Rest logic when being considered by the following timesheet period. This field is only used by the system where the Interpretation Rule has Apply Minimum Rest on Overtime = Yes.
CustomField.inlineHelpText: Used during interpretation processing to exclude an entry from Minimum Rest logic when being considered by the following timesheet period. This field is only used by the system where the Interpretation Rule has Apply Minimum Rest on Overtime = Yes.
CustomField.label: Do Not Apply Minimum Rest Logic
